Import shortcut
    @(command spacebar and start typing name of decorator, auto complete)

Implemented as functions

Declarative programming

May be attached to the following
    -Classes
    -Methods
    -Accessors
    -Properties
    -Parameters

Requires experimentalDecorators compiler option

Syntax
    function uiElement(target: Function) { do ui stuff }
    function deprecated( t: any, p: string, d: PropertyDescriptor) {}

        t : constructor
        p : what your decorating
        d :

    @uiElement   //syntax to use uiElement as decorator for contactform
    class ContactForm{
        @deprecated  //syntax to use deprecated as decorator for someoldmethod
        someOldMethod() {}
    }

